6.00	Paula_Ben-Gurion	Paula Ben-Gurion	Paula (Munweis or Monbesz) Ben-Gurion (Hebrew: ‎; 1892 – 1968) was the Russian-born wife of David Ben-Gurion the founding Prime Minister of Israel. They had three children together: Geula, Amos and Renana.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b1/Grave_of_David_Ben_Gurion_and_Paula_Munweis_in_Sde_Boker.jpg/220px-Grave_of_David_Ben_Gurion_and_Paula_Munweis_in_Sde_Boker.jpg
